data.name: xUpperCharLimit.ToolTip
data.value: Determine how many uppercase letters a player can have in their message if the message length is over 10 digits long. If they go over the set amount it sets their whole message to lowercase. Set to 1 for default, which is (rawMessage.Length / 2)

data.name: lCrashReportDisclaimer.Text
data.value: Crash reports are created when serious unexpected errors occur. Being able to receive crash reports helps identify bugs and improve fCraft! The report consists of the error information, OS and runtime versions, a copy of config.xml, and last 25 lines of the log file. Reports are confidential and are never displayed publicly.
